SELECT * FROM random_company_type_1 AS ct,  random_info_type_1 AS it,  random_movie_companies_1 AS mc,  random_movie_info_1 AS mi,  random_title_1 AS t  WHERE t.id = mi.movie_id  AND t.id = mc.movie_id  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id  AND ct.id = mc.company_type_id  AND it.id = mi.info_type_id  AND ct.kind = 'distributors'  AND mc.note LIKE '%USA%'  AND mc.note LIKE '%2012%'  AND mi.info IN ('$6,336,683 (USA) (17 March 2013)', 'FACT: Colonel Radl tells Mr. Devlin that he served on the Russian front, but he wears no ribbon for that campaign on his uniform.', '$37,162 (USA) (4 March 2012) (14 screens)', '$36,994,417 (USA) (7 December 2008)', 'Don Dieguito, Magdalena, Colombia')  AND t.production_year > 2005 LIMIT 5;
